Class logBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.tel.fer.lab1.query.logBaseListener

    ExpressionExtractor

    public class logBaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements logListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of logListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
